{"tid":1289219,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［拋磚引玉］ 7／7 高鐵站公安執法地圖","createTime":"2019-07-06T04:08:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-06T07:47:24.000Z","uid":273901,"like":37,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"217a688d71de6622e0a9063b65d437e0a84e7a09","tid":1289219,"uid":273901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T04:08:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">帶定頭盔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 強烈譴責暴力 愛國愛港</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<em>楊岳橋：車站內地口岸區「極敏感」<br />\n有立法會議員指出，高鐵站內設內地口岸區，執法標準存有太多不確定性，呼籲參與的市民要小心留意。</em><br />\nSource: <a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/pns/要聞/article/20190704/s00001/1562177423099/楊岳橋-車站內地口岸區「極敏感」\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%E8%A6%81%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190704%2Fs00001%2F1562177423099%2F%E6%A5%8A%E5%B2%B3%E6%A9%8B-%E8%BB%8A%E7%AB%99%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E5%8F%A3%E5%B2%B8%E5%8D%80%E3%80%8C%E6%A5%B5%E6%95%8F%E6%84%9F%E3%80%8D&d=5uNkoBKOFFInbKPjzc0vjeTO5ApsLFANoEfWU0iq%2Bkc%3D&h=dde9e332\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%E8%A6%81%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190704%2Fs00001%2F1562177423099%2F%E6%A5%8A%E5%B2%B3%E6%A9%8B-%E8%BB%8A%E7%AB%99%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E5%8F%A3%E5%B2%B8%E5%8D%80%E3%80%8C%E6%A5%B5%E6%95%8F%E6%84%9F%E3%80%8D&h=5d641bd0\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/pns/要聞/article/20190704/s00001/1562177423099/楊岳橋-車站內地口岸區「極敏感」</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">問1: 到底有幾敏感呢？</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">根據香港法例第632章 《廣深港高鐵(一地兩檢)條例》:</span></span><br />\n<br />\nSection 6.於內地口岸區的法律及管轄權<br />\n(1)除就保留事項外 &mdash;&mdash;<br />\n(a)就內地法律及香港法律於內地口岸區的適用而言；並<br />\n(b)就<span style=\"color: red;\">內地口岸區的管轄權</span>(包括司法管轄權)的劃分而言，<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><ins>內地口岸區的範圍，視為處於香港以外並處於內地以內。</ins></strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n(2)在1997年第6期《憲報第5號特別副刊》刊登的1997年7月1日《中華人民共和國國務院令》第221號*所公布的香港特別行政區行政區域界線，不受第(1)款影響。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">問2: 到底何謂內地口岸區？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">根據香港法例第632章 《廣深港高鐵(一地兩檢)條例》:</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">1) 車廂</span><br />\n<br />\nSection 5.車廂<br />\n(1)就本條例而言，高鐵香港段上營運中的客運列車(包括在行駛中、停留中和上下乘客期間的客運列車)的車廂，視為在西九龍站內地口岸區範圍之內。<br />\n(2)就第(1)款而言，在以下期間，客運列車並非營運中 &mdash;&mdash;<br />\n(a)客運列車在石崗列車停放處內的期間；或<br />\n(b)客運列車在由石崗列車停放處前往西九龍站的行程途中，或在由西九龍站前往石崗列車停放處的行程途中。<br />\n<br />\n=&gt; <span style=\"color: red;\">總之就咩車廂都唔好掂</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">2) 為咗大家唔好自行送中，正苦係條法例入面仲附上平面圖同橫切面圖俾大家參考</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0jnVbyD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0jnVbyD.png&h=c2f481af&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iTUP0r2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiTUP0r2.png&h=6eb35c1b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有蘋果日報簡易版：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Vssuf1g.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVssuf1g.png&h=13e88816&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n同香港01簡易版：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ub5SYeJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fub5SYeJ.png&h=ae3e4386&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">參觀高鐵站嘅朋友千祈唔好行錯路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"3895442971eae43c42c1c5b213a957912f4bc5b0","tid":1289219,"uid":273901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T04:10:31.000Z","msg":"Pushh"},{"pid":"494cd41e4e5be654ad7e1ec16ec880817ba67db2","tid":1289219,"uid":263197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T04:10:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40618d85c42be9be7f77e0a4df53d82c4d718887","tid":1289219,"uid":273901,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T04:11:35.000Z","msg":"溫好書先行萬里路"},{"pid":"8de51be7fda328997e6831df6550e976076e948c","tid":1289219,"uid":90873,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T04:12:23.000Z","msg":"唔好入左唔應該入既範圍<br />\n大家小心"},{"pid":"528761a5432c1c43de9530e5736b4dc145114a61","tid":1289219,"uid":156936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"40618d85c42be9be7f77e0a4df53d82c4d718887","tid":1289219,"uid":273901,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T04:11:35.000Z","msg":"溫好書先行萬里路"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T04:13:42.000Z","msg":"十卜地圖撚, 推到上熱門"},{"pid":"145665ac9916196682e779060bd9073fd6afd2dd","tid":1289219,"uid":249187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T04:13:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a2a0994b5183bfa2f5f405940e5a7aec379097d6","tid":1289219,"uid":197470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T04:15:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4fd2d05ed877caa9d8de819c97a1c626b8202cb6","tid":1289219,"uid":263944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T04:15:29.000Z","msg":"PUSH"},{"pid":"86e71a52dcf72fdcf64b10bd89bcb7fa35bfd30b","tid":1289219,"uid":156936,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T04:16:00.000Z","msg":"咁落左月台出手, 係唔係當大陸犯法, 出返閘到香港就無事"},{"pid":"cd3223b96662e7d108c99549bfb87f6a17b2b714","tid":1289219,"uid":79249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T04:16:31.000Z","msg":"<pre><code data-type=\"\">我無嘢講 我要見律師 我要驗傷 我唔解鎖電話 我唔簽任何文件\n1. 立即撤回送中條例\n2. 除消暴動定義\n3. 不再追究義士\n4. 成立獨立調查\n5. 真雙普選</code></pre>"},{"pid":"8062c8e68997cd03bb1b0ed0f2bbb4e83867cb95","tid":1289219,"uid":47042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T04:17:40.000Z","msg":"好簡單，唔好過安檢嗰度閘已經夠<br />\n<br />\n有覺悟另計"},{"pid":"94c619e6a8a4b3038eed75efd6f863768cc61aa4","tid":1289219,"uid":13013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T04:20:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4aa1f6b60476822ca209a2a764c38a598c740a8","tid":1289219,"uid":273901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T05:00:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8ad40aa2601119c61c29643937fa3710692add8b","tid":1289219,"uid":245484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T05:03:22.000Z","msg":"一定一定要保證撤退路線<br />\n比狗推左落去就死撚硬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d63b58cec518dae99987f69110343c28851c18b","tid":1289219,"uid":89627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T05:47:42.000Z","msg":"我無嘢講 我要見律師 我要驗傷 我唔解鎖電話 我唔簽任何文件"},{"pid":"16e1cfd7d1ddc346601f0fe86602b811f900694a","tid":1289219,"uid":268276,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"86e71a52dcf72fdcf64b10bd89bcb7fa35bfd30b","tid":1289219,"uid":156936,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T04:16:00.000Z","msg":"咁落左月台出手, 係唔係當大陸犯法, 出返閘到香港就無事"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T05:52:44.000Z","msg":"切勿自行送中，多謝合作<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"178e3ca668a2e5256a4b98ff942070125cba2067","tid":1289219,"uid":273163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T06:20:16.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n<code>五大訴求\n\n一、徹底撤回修例\n\n二、收回暴動定義\n\n三、撤銷對今為所有反送中抗爭者控罪\n\n四、徹底追究警隊濫權情況\n\n五、以行政命令解散立法會，立即實行雙真普選</code>"},{"pid":"f20892f989f12c29de62dfd0bb75e79e5c12ffec","tid":1289219,"uid":50891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T06:22:55.000Z","msg":"我冇野講"},{"pid":"c692e02daf88e0ab67fe736fa874d71d0b7f63ee","tid":1289219,"uid":261043,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T06:29:24.000Z","msg":"簡單D講唔入閘就得，我要排隊問路，我要研究點買飛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5e395de533dce4ce76bb8da92409ce68440763b","tid":1289219,"uid":18948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T06:29:58.000Z","msg":"香港人出入境自由由基本法保障<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d504953a2c1f321ead1ff656d7d1eb634be9452","tid":1289219,"uid":18948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d5e395de533dce4ce76bb8da92409ce68440763b","tid":1289219,"uid":18948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T06:29:58.000Z","msg":"香港人出入境自由由基本法保障<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T06:33:45.000Z","msg":"葉劉淑儀今早於商台節目解釋，入境條例中「無一條罪行叫無持有效旅行證件離境」；至於李波沒用回鄉卡出境，她指「出境（香港）唔係睇回鄉卡，入境（內地）先睇回鄉卡，你無回鄉卡唔關我事架。陸地或港口口岸出境，唔睇你回鄉卡，睇你有無身分證之嘛」。<br />\n<br />\n葉劉淑儀強調，香港永久居民如何出境「唔會係一個問題」，「睇唔到會點樣構成罪行。無非法出境說法」。她又說，即使港人在外地遺失了身分證，「都好容易入返來（香港）」，只要向入境處說自己遺失了身分證便可。<br />\n<br />\n葉劉淑儀又說，如離境時不接受入境人員檢查，可能觸犯入境條例；不經口岸進入禁區，亦可能犯禁區條例，但重申「無永久性居民未經許可出入境條例，係無嘅」。<br />\n<br />\n入境處長陳國基昨亦稱，香港永久居民以自己方式出入境不會被控「非法出入境」，但可能涉及違反其他條例。"},{"pid":"7897bb367fca1a6a979301d8ecc3f80bc0d74781","tid":1289219,"uid":31405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T06:37:17.000Z","msg":"我係管轄權大叫平反64會點<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2353a44ac4359e0b968a95b2ed4ec8be1d2e726","tid":1289219,"uid":60423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7897bb367fca1a6a979301d8ecc3f80bc0d74781","tid":1289219,"uid":31405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T06:37:17.000Z","msg":"我係管轄權大叫平反64會點<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T06:44:03.000Z","msg":"大叫平反64 公安死全家 習近平戇鳩無撚用落地獄<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />係咪無事"},{"pid":"193a1cc73d2aa50213448aed79555cbae54e199f","tid":1289219,"uid":137480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T06:44:40.000Z","msg":"小心D你唔過去姐但行近左班大陸狗拉你過去<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}